Package: robgpu
Version: 0.0.0
Title: Robust Statistics and Tools on GPU
Author: Roland Boubela <roland.boubela@gmail.com>, Andreas Alfons <alfons@ese.eur.nl>
Maintainer: Roland Boubela <roland.boubela@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0),Rcpp (>= 0.10.4)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
SystemRequirements: Nvidia's CUDA toolkit (>= release 5.5)
Description: This package implements parallelized versions of some 
        tools (e.g. colwise mean, correlation) and robust statistical 
        methods on GPUs.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/robgpu
NeedsCompilation: yes

